kirc
====

A tiny IRC client written in POSIX C99. 

Installation
------------

Build and install from source:
    
    git clone https://github.com/mcpcpc/kirc
    cd kirc
    make
    make install

Usage
-----

Consult `man kirc` for a complete explanation and list of arguments

    kirc [-s hostname] [-p port] [-c channels] [-n nickname] 
         [-r realname] [-u username] [-k password] [-a token] 
         [-x command] [-o logfile] [-e|v|V]

Support Documentation
---------------------

Please refer to the official Support Documention [0] for examples, 
troubleshooting and use cases.
    
    https://mcpcpc.github.io/kirc/documentation.html

